&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Background in AI/ML technologies or enterprise software&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Experience scaling partnerships in emerging or fast-moving technology markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;font-claude-response-body whitespace-normal break-words pl-2&quot;&gt;Track record of building enterprise GTM strategies in a zero-to-one or foundational capacity&lt;/li&gt;
